{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"299786d771","title":"关于做好第二个五年计划布局和开好军委会议问题给邓小平的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"09c4c1a51d","index":0,"year":1958,"month":6,"day":7,"articleId":"299786d771"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"5bd9678625","name":"邓小平","type":"人物"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji39","name":"毛泽东全集第39卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/39-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji39":{"comments":[{"id":"a43058b720","publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"299786d771","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"邓小平，当时任中共中央总书记、国务院副总理、中共中央军委委员。"},{"id":"3f5c28ab02","publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"299786d771","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"德怀，即彭德怀，当时任中共中央军委委员、国务院副总理兼国防部部长。"},{"id":"b1b8edcb62","publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"299786d771","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指正在召开的军委扩大会议。这次会议于1958年5月27日至7月22日在北京举行。会议讨论了当前局势、国防工作和今后的建军方针。"}],"contents":[{"id":"707abba70a","type":"title","text":"关于做好第二个五年计划布局和开好军委会议问题给邓小平的信","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"299786d771"},{"id":"a43058b720","type":"paragraph","text":"小平同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"299786d771"},{"id":"3f5c28ab02","type":"paragraph","text":"六、七两月份，你应做两件事：（一）第二个五年计划的布局，如你自己所提的；（二）帮助德怀以同志将军事会议开好，关键是本月一个月，宜与彭等少数同志每三天商量一次。大事抓起来干多快好省。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"299786d771"},{"id":"b1b8edcb62","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"299786d771"},{"id":"769f54a24d","type":"paragraph","text":"六月七日上午四时","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"299786d771"},{"id":"6b88dcdbcd","type":"paragraph","text":"军事会上，你应准备去讲一次话，时机可在结尾的时候","in